schools.name: Woodlawn High Center For Pre-Eng. Res.

data.description: Welcome to this charming turn-key ready split-level home situated on a tranquil street, conveniently positioned near shopping centers, public transportation, and 695. The main level features three inviting well-lit carpeted bedrooms with ample storage, complemented by a full bath with a tub/shower. Notably, the master bedroom and kitchen are bathed in wonderful morning sunlight, while the cozy living room is illuminated by the warm evening sun, creating an ideal space for relaxation and entertainment. The eat-in kitchen is equipped with excellent appliances and provides easy access to both the dining room and a beautiful deck with a scenic view of the well-maintained and fenced backyard.  The studded, spacious walk-out basement offers versatility for various uses such as a kids' playroom, exercise room, office, workshop, or any other purpose you may require. The front and backyard are generously sized and adaptable for a variety of uses. The HVAC system is diligently maintained twice a year by a professional home maintenance company.  PROFESSIONAL PHOTOS WILL BE PROVIDED ON OR BEFORE 12/9
